69.7	Hideo_Kojima	Hideo Kojima	Hideo Kojima Kojima Hideo, born August 24, 1963) is a Japanese game director originally employed at Konami. He is currently the director of Kojima Productions and was promoted to Vice President of Konami Digital Entertainment in early 2011. His previous positions include being vice president of Konami Computer Entertainment Japan.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d0/Kojima_Hideo.jpg/220px-Kojima_Hideo.jpg
